# CLI entry directory

Reserved for the fleet-e2e-toy CLI. Architecture decisions for this directory
are recorded in beads task gh-toy-80w.1 (notes). Scaffolding of
src/cli/index.ts happens in gh-toy-80w.2.

Summary of decisions (see `bd show gh-toy-80w.1` for full notes):
- Framework: yargs (already in package-lock.json transitively, v17.7.2)
- HTTP client: built-in global fetch (Node >= 18)
- Entry: src/cli/index.ts -> compiles to dist/cli/index.js via existing tsc config
- Binary: package.json bin = { "fleet-e2e-toy": "dist/cli/index.js" }
